Module it.polimi.ingsw

Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.gamestates

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGameState
    An abstract class that can be implemented by the states.
    EndGame
    The class representing the last state of game which ends it.
    OngoingGame
    The class representing the state of the game in which a player can control his worker and eventually win or lose.
    PreGodsGame
    The class representing the state of game in which the challenger chooses the gods from the deck and players choose from the challenger list a god to use in the game.
    PreInitGame
    The class representing the first state of game which precedes the start.
    PreWorkersGame
    The class representing the state of game in which the players choose where to spawn their workers and spans them
